description: I.D.C.A.S. came out a year ago (on my 27th birthday) as the first single release off Death Ain’t That Bad. In the song I sample a voice note I recorded of myself yelling “I Don’t Care About Shit That I Can’t Stay In Control Of” during an anxiety attack in 2019. After sharing the song with Tara at the beginning of 2020, she sent me this animatic as a lyric video pitch and we went with it. Care about the things you can control and don’t stress about what you cannot.
